**  NAME  **
"0":DELETE
"1":CHANGE
"2":ADD
**  MSG  **
01:INPUT ERROR.
02:UNIT PRICE MASTER FILE NOT FOUND.
03:UNIT PRICE MASTER FILE FOUND.
04:INPUTED NUMBER IS INCORRECT.
05:DATA OVERLAP.
06:INCORRECT DATE.
07:DETAIL M/F <CODE COMPLETION> NOT FOUND.
08:INPUT ERROR. ONLY THE LATEST RECORD CAN BE ERASED.
09:FINISHED MATERIAL MASTER DOES NOT EXIST.
10:ROD MATERIAL MASTER DOES NOT EXIST.
11:PART TYPE INCORRECT
12:PLEASE INPUT VENDOR CODE
13:PLEASE INPUT START DATE
14:PLEASE INPUT END DATE
15:PLEASE INPUT UNIT PRICE
